milestones.description: Derek Randall has broken the record for most catches (8) in ODIs, going past Tony Greig's 7
Lance Cairns has broken the record for most sixes (7) in ODIs for NZ, going past Ken Wadsworth's 3
Lance Cairns has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for NZ, going past Hadlee's 2
Lance Cairns has conceded the most runs in an innings (84) in ODIs for NZ, going past Bevan Congdon's record of 77
Lance Cairns has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs, going past Clive Lloyd's 3
Derek Randall has broken the record for most catches (8) in ODIs for ENG, going past Tony Greig's 7
Lance Cairns has conceded the most runs in an innings (84) in ODIs, going past Karsan Ghavri's record of 83
Collinge has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (15) for NZ, going past Glenn Turner
Clive Radley and David Gower's 105-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 103 between Mike Denness and David Lloyd
